✅ Benefits of FlatList in React Native (Summary):
High Performance – Renders only visible items (virtualization), great for large lists.

Lazy Loading – Loads items as needed, improving load time.

Built-in Features – Supports pull-to-refresh, pagination, headers/footers, and empty states.

Clean Code – Easier to manage and customize list items.

Smooth UX – Better scrolling and memory management than ScrollView.

Use FlatList when dealing with dynamic or large datasets.